public class EnergySavingFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataCenterFactory

This class implements the interface DataCenterFactory, that is to say, LoadBalanceFactory would follow the defined process of. While for the instance of EnergySavingFactory, it can produce different composition for different requests creating approaches, scheduling algorithms, comparison indices.
